snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online - Official Welcome to The Elder Scrolls Online Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn about The Elder Scrolls Online in this overview trailer that gives a breakdown of what you can expect with gameplay and features, including a look at character creation and progression, group activities, crafting, housing, and more.

The Elder Scrolls Online is available now on PC, Mac, Stadia, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, and PlayStation 4.

#IGN #ESO
